        <abstract>
            <p>Has succeeded in obtaining Assistant Keeper’s post.</p>
            <p>Believes it would be interesting and valuable to study the variation in organs such as scent-fans and "strigillating" [stridulating?] organs among related species of Lepidoptera.</p>
